caller_intent: Maria Vialon wants to add a third vehicle to her insurance policy and inquire about the impact on her premium.
resolution_steps: Agent Gina verifies Maria's identity and policy details (address, name, existing vehicles).
Maria provides vehicle details: 2001 Ford truck with VIN 1FTRW07L01K36821.
Agent confirms coverage type (liability-only) and no additional drivers.
Agent checks rate impact and informs Maria of the new monthly payment ($1,516.60).
Maria confirms no further requests and ends the call.
knowledge_required: Vehicle addition process for insurance policies
summary: Maria Vialon contacted Alliance Insurance to add a third vehicle (2001 Ford truck) to her policy. Agent Gina collected vehicle details, confirmed liability coverage, and informed Maria of a rate increase to $1,516.60/month. The call concluded with Maria confirming no further requests.
